OL,5,G1900 Aistear An Amhrain
OL,6,     FThe series finale of Aistear an
OL,7,     FAmhrain explores the remarkable
OL,8,     Fhistory and cultural legacy of one
OL,9,     Fof Ireland's best-loved Irish
OL,10,     Flanguage songs, An Poc ar Buile.
OL,11,G1930 Cheap Irish Homes
OL,12,     FMaggie and Kieran head to Cork to
OL,13,     Fhelp South African natives Erin
OL,14,     Fand Louis, who have fallen in love
OL,15,     Fwith Ireland to find a place that
OL,16,     Fthey can call their own.
OL,17,G2000 Fair City
OL,18,     FWhen Emma's plan goes ahead it
OL,19,     Fspells disaster for Tommy. Carol's
OL,20,     Funder pressure to be honest with
OL,21,     FDenise. Lorcan fears Carol is
OL,22,     Fhiding something terrible.
